#

Italian Meat and Bean Stew

45 min
$10
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodOne-PotHearty

Description

A hearty and flavorful stew packed with tender meat and nutritious beans, perfect for a cozy meal.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • canned cannellini beans: 2 cans (15 oz each)
  • diced tomatoes: 1 can (14.5 oz)
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • italian seasoning: 2 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • chicken broth: 2 cups
  • spinach (optional): 2 cups, fresh
